msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Commodore - VIC-20 (VICE xvic)"
msgstr "Commodore - VIC-20 (VICE xvic)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "VICE stands for the Versatile Commodore Emulator. The current version emulates the C64, the C64DTV, the C128, the VIC20, practically all PET models, the PLUS4 and the CBM-II (aka C610/C510)."
msgstr "VICE je zkratka pro Versatile Commodore Emulator. Aktuální verze emuluje C64, C64DTV, C128, VIC20, prakticky všechny modely PET, PLUS4 a CBM-II (také C610/C510)."

